        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 5:59AM EDT until June 8 at 6:30AM EDT by NWS Wakefield VA</headline>
        <description>At 559 AM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Jarratt, or
near Purdy, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to vehicles is possible. Expect wind damage to
trees and powerlines.

This severe storm will be near...
Jarratt around 605 AM EDT.

Other locations impacted by this severe thunderstorm include Adams
Grove, Gray, Grizzard, Fields Crossroads, Emporia Reservoir, Cowie
Corner, Hilda, Owens, Mason, and Durand.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
